column5: Pics from fishing docks at Rice, then went out on Stony the next weekend
Last one. and I guess I'll upload them somewhere next time so I don't have to make more replies.  I'm a new member, long time browser on the forum.  Thanks for all the info I got from OFC!
a lot of us use www.photobucket.com
welcome to the forum, looks like you are doing well over at rice lake.
Welcome aboard Kwan.  It looks like you already know how much we like pics.
Great pics Kwan, keep 'em coming and welcome aboard.
welcome to the board kwan !!! fish as often as you can with dad. its something you will remember forever
Good show, keep catching my friend! Wish I had a Dad to fish with yet my son is in training as of this moment!
Welcome aboard Kwan and Dad.  Looks like a great day on Rice for you guys. Thanks for posting your report.
Welcome aboard & nice Smallie keep um coming Richard
I really like father and son reports. Looks like you guys did ok. Thanks for sharing.
Welcome aboard great first post always great to see father and son out fishing
Great first post Kwan Father son duo style just doesn't get any better then that Welcome to OFC and thanks for sharing!!! Leechman
Welcome aboard Kwan . . . thanks for leading with a report
